{"tid":395804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"紋身男apm搶的士 輾司機掟爆iPhone","createTime":"2017-09-11T06:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T08:27:42.000Z","uid":34498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9b8b6bbf0a3caf208205e9aba7ea20fafa81de","tid":395804,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/09/10/3438112/20170910_ccm_03v30_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F3438112%2F20170910_ccm_03v30_w.mp4&d=zm1YLSEXK%2Bh7fiA9yBSUQV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=309d94dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/09/10/3438112/20170910_ccm_03v30_w.mp4</a><br />\n <br />\n凌晨約1時，觀塘apm對開，一名有醉意姓翁26歲紋身男子截乘的士，疑酒醉與姓周49歲司機爭執，並爬上前座企圖毆打司機，司機立即下車及走到前座乘客位，開門企圖將醉漢拖落車，兩人互相拉扯，醉漢移往司機位，並開動的士。<br />\n<br />\n其時的士往後溜動，司機馬上走到司機位外，伸腳入內企圖踩腳掣煞停，不料被醉漢推出車外，腳掌並被車輪輾過，的士倒後行駛，左車尾更撞倒鐵欄才停下。其時途人見兩人爭執已報警。救護員首先到場，將醉男帶到救護車上，其間他扯斷的士水撥及踢爛的士左前指揮燈。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，其後他在救護車上情緒失控，將iPhone手機掟落地，產生爆炸發出隆然巨響，警員發現一湧而上，合力將他制服，並五花大綁送院。警方調查發現，醉漢涉嫌襲擊、偷車及刑毀，被警方拘捕。的士司機受傷送院。<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線：63836568 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1504990620_6d4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1504990620_6d4b.jpg&h=e968cbfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n (鄭文輝攝) <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1504990609_0f7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1504990609_0f7c.jpg&h=96f4239e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 紋身男子被警方拘捕。(鄭文輝攝) <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1504990630_947a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1504990630_947a.jpg&h=e9896320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 警員撿走iPhone手機。(鄭文輝攝) <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1504990645_f3c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1504990645_f3c1.jpg&h=e269abd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 的士司機協助調查。(鄭文輝攝) <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1504990659_144e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1504990659_144e.jpg&h=91daf104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 的士失控撞欄，警員在場調查。(鄭文輝攝) <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1504990667_746a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1504990667_746a.jpg&h=55543450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n (鄭文輝攝) <br />\n <br />\nsource : <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2F&d=zm1YLSEXK%2Bh7fiA9yBSUQV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a793e2cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2F&h=7a93f946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將iPhone手機掟落地，產生爆炸發出隆然巨響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"03966913d2000e1d6856e7e2ab08b80bf2f31979","tid":395804,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"DC9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377f7d996613974649294c22662122775a9f5e4e","tid":395804,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT